  "detailed_description": "Experience the Russian roulette game with friends with a small twist that will make the classic game more strategic and unpredictable, with some chaos involved in it...<br><br>Spice things up by incorporation <strong>special objects</strong> mid-round, offering advantages and disadvantages to players. Special objects such as a helmet that protects the players from the shot! or skip your turn if that's your way of doing things...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874860/extras/e7df6b253f958ae63d1a0e2e0d52c566.poster.avif?t=1731968639\" width=558 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874860/extras/e7df6b253f958ae63d1a0e2e0d52c566.webm?t=1731968639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874860/extras/e7df6b253f958ae63d1a0e2e0d52c566.mp4?t=1731968639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Shoot your fellas to win!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874860/extras/3decf02612b52d6566d9146f185c90e5.poster.avif?t=1731968639\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874860/extras/3decf02612b52d6566d9146f185c90e5.webm?t=1731968639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874860/extras/3decf02612b52d6566d9146f185c90e5.mp4?t=1731968639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Every time you risk shooting yourself (and you don't die), you get a coin. The coin can then be used to strategically target and shoot other players.<br><br>Are you ready to paint the walls red?",
